.png" alt="International Accolades"><hgroup><h2 class="sub">International Accolades</h2><h3 class="super">高分产品</h3></hgroup><p>美国著名葡萄酒评论家罗伯特·帕克高评分产品</p><p>权威杂志《葡萄酒倡导家》高评分产品</p><p>权威杂志《葡萄酒鉴赏家》高评分产品</p></div><div class="card"><img class="image" src="images/lmported.png" alt="Authentic Appellation"><hgroup><h2 class="sub">Authentic Appellation</h2><h3 class="super">原庄原瓶进口</h3></hgroup><p>从葡萄种植、酿造生产、进出口物流到销售渠道、</p><p>售后服务等全程层层精挑细选</p></div></div></div></section><section id="contact"><hgroup><h2 class="super">CONTACT</h2><h3 class="sub">联系我们</h3></hgroup><div class="content"><div class="company"><img src="images/contact.png" alt="苏州尚葡信息科技有限公司"></div><div class="qrcode"><figure><img src="images/official.png" alt="官方微信服务号"><figcaption>官方微信<br>服务号</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="images/subscription.png" alt="官方微信订阅号"><figcaption>官方微信<br>订阅号</figcaption></figure></div></div></section><footer class="foot"><div style="text-align:center;width:100%;"><a href="http://m.kuaidi100.com" style="color:white;" target="_blank">快递查询</a></div><p>Copyright &copy; 2016 - All Rights Reserved - Simplywine Information Technology Co. , Ltd. - 苏州尚葡信息科技有限公司版权所有</p><p><a href="http://www.miitbeian.gov.cn/">苏ICP备16026201号</a></p></footer></div></body></html>
